00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,549
Good evening, we bring you breaking developments tonight.

00:00:02,549 --> 00:00:05,859
A major diplomatic event is unfolding in New Delhi as Vladimir Putin,

00:00:05,859 --> 00:00:09,259
President of Russia, lands in India for a high-stakes two-day visit.

00:00:09,259 --> 00:00:13,390
At precisely 6.035 pm local time, Putin arrived at the capital,

00:00:13,390 --> 00:00:16,429
greeted personally by Narendra Modi, a rare warm welcome,

00:00:16,429 --> 00:00:20,170
complete with a hug and handshake, signaling the special importance of this visit.

00:00:20,170 --> 00:00:20,660
Right!

00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:22,460
..

00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:26,800
Reports say the Russian president is accompanied not only by senior ministers,

00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:31,799
but also by a large business delegation underscoring that beyond politics, commerce, trade, commerce, trade,

00:00:31,799 --> 00:00:33,920
and industry are high on the agenda.

00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:38,469
From the airport, port leaders proceeded directly to the official residence of Loke Kalyanmar.

00:00:38,469 --> 00:00:41,900
And overnight, Prime Minister Modi will host a private dinner in honour of President Putin.

00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:44,189
This dinner revives the tradition.

00:00:44,189 --> 00:00:49,329
During each summit, such informal gatherings help cement personal rapport between leaders here,

00:00:49,329 --> 00:00:51,359
beyond the stiff protocol of formal meetings.

00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:55,670
Hmm, ahead of this visit, New Delhi has been transformed.

00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:59,569
Billboards and hoardings declaring Indo-Russian friendship taught major roads.

00:00:59,569 --> 00:01:03,810
The atmosphere signals the warming of ties even in fraught global times.

00:01:03,810 --> 00:01:10,500
That symbolism matters. This is the first time President Putin is visiting India since the onset of the war in Ukraine nearly four years ago.

00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:15,150
Ex-security in the capital has been stepped up to unprecedented levels.

00:01:15,150 --> 00:01:19,890
So, cross-sectors, sky and ground agencies remain on high alert.

00:01:19,890 --> 00:01:22,870
Authorities have tightly sealed the roots of the President's movement.

00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:30,450
Sensitive locations have been secured and additional personnel from both national and local agencies deployed, reflecting the sensitivity of this visit.

00:01:30,450 --> 00:01:37,879
Tomorrow, the heart of the visit, the two leaders will meet at Hyderabad House for the 23rd Annual Summit between India and Russia.

00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:44,719
Agenda spans a gamut, from defence cooperation, energy supplies, nuclear power collaboration, arms to trade, healthcare and even labour mobility.

00:01:44,719 --> 00:01:49,420
Right before this visit began, the Russian parliament ratified a major military logistics

00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:53,400
pact, the reciprocal exchange of logistics support are a loss, allowing armed forces

00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:58,629
of both nations to use each other's facilities for exercises, humanitarian assets and disaster

00:01:58,629 --> 00:02:00,069
relief cooperation.

00:02:00,069 --> 00:02:04,379
Apart from defense, the two countries are poised to deepen cooperation in civilian nuclear

00:02:04,379 --> 00:02:04,939
energy.

00:02:04,939 --> 00:02:08,840
Government sources confirm pending agreements potentially giving a fresh push to projects

00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,840
like Rosatom back to reactors in India.

00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:17,319
India. Such energy deals, especially in non-military nuclear power, may help address India's long-term

00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:21,219
energy needs, a move that could reshape the strategic balance of energy security in South

00:02:21,219 --> 00:02:21,860
Asia.

00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:26,180
Economy and trade also featured prominently. Delegations from both sides are expected to

00:02:26,180 --> 00:02:29,340
assign deans across pharmaceuticals, manufacturing, textiles and labour mobility.

00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:29,800
.

